@startuml Parts Lifecycle

[*] --> Sourced : Part found
Sourced --> Ordered : Place order
Ordered --> InTransit : Shipped
InTransit --> Received : Delivered
Received --> QualityCheck : Inspect
QualityCheck --> Installed : Pass
QualityCheck --> Returned : Fail
Installed --> [*] : Complete

Received --> Stored : Hold for later
Stored --> Installed : Ready to install

note right of QualityCheck
  Verify correct part
  Check condition
  Test fit if possible
end note

@enduml
